name: Get your own logo / message / name / art and more on a T-shirt and many other items with SIKA prints
description:
Top quality, low price... Trust SIKA prints!

GET IN TOUCH FOR YOUR PERSONAL QUOTE...

07779560505 / sikastudios@hotmail.co.uk

We have been running a successful clothing label for over 5 years and have first hand experience in outsourcing/printing and the issues faced by you the customer. This is why we have taken great effort to be able to provide a friendly and high quality printing service to suit all needs and budgets; including...

INDIVIDUAL QUOTES... To keep your costs down and your satisfaction high we deal with every order individually and maintain the contact through the order, available via e-mail or phone from a friendly SIKA printer

MULTI/MIXED MEDIUM PRINTING... Screen/vinyl/ink/puff/reflective/glow in the dark and a lot more!

PICTURE/POSTAL CHECK... Check the final product before it goes into a full print run! Either by viewing a pictures of it online or by getting a sample t-shirt posted to you

FREE MISS PRINTS... If there are any T-shirts that we have printed and are not up to our super high standards. We will put them in on top your order, free of charge!

VARIED THICKNESS OF PRINTS... To suit different styles of prints (e.g. hip hop)

SIKA DESIGNS... We have a team of top quality unique artists and graphic designers ready to put your thoughts into print

CUSTOM LABELS... We can design/print/sew your own labels in garments

LABEL REMOVAL... Available on certain products

PACKAGING... Available in many different forms

PRINT ON YOUR OWN ITEMS... Just post them to us and we can do the rest

FREE SIKA PROMO... We can advertise your brand and print to our massive network or fans and followers of our parent company (SIKA studios)

For more info... Please send an e-mail to sikastudios@hotmail.co.uk or contact us via our SIKA prints page on facebook by copying and pasting the link below into your address bar...

http://www.facebook.com/pages/SIKA-prints/142784952503779?fref=ts

name: Brothers Of The Stone - CD
description:
CD of the brand new Brothers Of The Stone 14 track album! The Brothers Of The Stone are Leaf Dog & BVA with Illinformed on production! The album features Reef The Lost Cauze, Vinnie Paz, KRS-One, Beast 1333, Fliptrix, Smellington Piff, Eric The Red, Tommy Dockerz, Jack Jetson & DJ Sammy B-Side.

CD comes shrink wrapped in plastic jewel case with 4 page booklet.

name: Dead Players CD
description:
CD of the brand new Dead Players 12 track album! Dead Players are Jam Baxter & Dabbla with GhostTown on production! The album features Dirty Dike, Edward Scissortongue & Parly B.

CD comes shrink wrapped in Digi pack with 8 page booklet.

name: Dirty Dike - Return Of The Twat CD
description:
Dirty Dikes 13 track album 'Return Of The Twat'.

The album is produced, mixed and mastered by Naive & Pete Cannon. Features from Ronnie Bosh, Jam Baxter, Ed Scissortongue, BVA, Mr Key, Fliptrix, Leaf Dog, Verb T, Dabbla, DatKid, Stig Of The Dump, Dr. Syntax & DJ Manipulate.

Comes in full colour 6 panel digi pack casing, shrink wrapped.

name: Fliptrix - Third Eye of the Storm CD
description: Fliptrix - Third Eye Of The Storm (16 TRACK ALBUM) Ft. Jehst, Farma G, Jam Baxter, Verb T, Buggsy & Ramson Badbonez. Production by Chemo, 184, Leaf Dog, Jon Phonics, Medison, Naive, Runone, ExtraTeless, Mr Boss, Dillijence, Reklews, Kerem Fraiche & Kontigo. The CD comes with big fold out artwork and a 16 page booklet containing all Fliptrix's lyrics, imagery & more!

name: Jam Baxter - The Gruesome Features CD
description:
Jam Baxter's project entitled 'The Gruesome Features' featuring classic UK talent such as Chester P, Ramson Badbonez, Dirty Dike, Fliptrix, Verb T, Ronnie Bosh, Mowgli, Mr Key, DJ Sammy B-Side and more!

Digi pack CD with 8 page booklet containing visuals and selected lyrics.
